{"cat":"notebook","desc":"REVIEW
 
Sony is so confident that the VAIO S is a superior 
ultraportable laptop that the company proudly compares the notebook to 
Apple's 13-inch MacBook Pro. And in a lot of ways this notebook is 
better, thanks to a lighter weight, higher-resolution display, more 
storage space, and a Blu-ray drive. ","id":9,"img":"imgs/sony_vaio_5.jpg","price":790.0,"title":"Sony vaio i7

Introduction
The goal of this performance testing is to ensure that JPet Store, an e-commerce web application, provides a seamless user experience under typical and increasing user loads. The objective is to validate that the system can handle expected traffic levels smoothly and identify any performance bottlenecks.
Vision
Validate that the application remains responsive, stable, and scalable under growing user traffic. Ensure that the most critical user flowsâ€”browsing, adding to cart, and checkoutâ€”respond within acceptable time limits.

50 Users
100 Users
200 Users
The goal is to determine whether the system performs within acceptable thresholds across all core functionalities.

","id":2,"img":"imgs/Lumia_1520.jpg","price":820.0,"title":"Nokia lumia 1520"},{"cat":"phone","desc":"The Motorola Google Nexus 6 is powered by 2.7GHz quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 805 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM.","id":3,"img":"imgs/Nexus_6.jpg","price":650.0,"title":"Nexus 6"},{"cat":"phone","desc":"The Samsung Galaxy S7 is powered by 1.6GHz octa-core it comes with 4GB

 storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card. ","id":7,"img":"imgs/HTC_M9.jpg","price":700.0,"title":"HTC One M9"},{"cat":"notebook","desc":"Sony is so confident that the VAIO S is a superior ultraportable laptop

better, thanks to a lighter weight, higher-resolution display, more 
storage space, and a Blu-ray drive. ","id":9,"img":"imgs/sony_vaio_5.jpg","price":790.0,"title":"Sony vaio i7
"}],"LastEvaluatedKey":{"id":"9"}}
